column2:
"I know, you probably think I'm pathetic,
but that's just the way I am."
"I wouldn't have made it this far without you."

"I want to thank you for all you've done so far.
Let's head out together again, and I'll thank
you many times over!"

"はー……
情けない話だけど
こればっかりは仕方ねーよな。"

"ほんと、お前がいなかったら
おれ一人じゃどうにもなんねーよ。"

"いつもサンキュな！
よっし、いっちょガツンと行くか！"
